The significance of the number 5 is something to really think about this season! I gotta admit first things first that I don’t watch the women’s football, not that I don’t want to but there’s no streaming service that stream women’s sports except for UFC(I mean there are but one subscription is enough for me). I’m saying this because I might miss some important match where we won 5 goals up too.

Anyway, every important match we win by scoring 5 goals! 
We beat Man City by 5 goals, after Haaland’s unnecessary words to Arteta and MLS.

We Beat Real Madrid and their Ramontada 5-1, again important match even by putting what’s at stake aside, these two matches are where rival fans barks the most!

Now the WFC also won 3-0 against Madrid and I might be reaching here but the total score was 5 with Madrid’s 2 goals in first leg. And now our women won 5goals up again.

And the postcode of course, N5!
